title: Violence in Palestinian town described as 'a pogrom' by Israeli military commander
description: A senior commander in the Israeli military has described the violence by Israeli settlers in the Palestinian town of Hawara on Sunday night as "a pogrom".

title: China accuses US of 'abusing state power' over TikTok ban
description: China has denounced the US over its TikTok bans, saying it has been "abusing state power".

title: NATO membership 'top priority' for Sweden and Finland
description: NATO membership for Sweden and Finland is a "top priority", according to its secretary general, Jens Stoltenberg.

title: Mafia boss breaks out of prison using bed sheets
description: A mafia boss has broken out of a Sardinian prison using a rudimentary method of escape.

title: American-Israeli citizen identified as West Bank shooting victim
description: A man killed in the West Bank on Monday has been identified as a 26-year-old American-Israeli citizen, Elan Ganeles.

title: Mallorca hit by heavy snow as Storm Juliette brings freezing temperatures to Spain
description: Heavy snow has hit the Spanish island of Mallorca, with Storm Juliette sweeping across the country.

title: 'Smugglers' charged €8,000 each for migrants' 'voyage of death' to southern Italy
description: Smugglers allegedly charged €8,000 (£7,000) each for the "voyage of death" from Turkey to Italy in which at least 65 people died.

title: Iranian female pupils poisoned in classrooms in suspected plan to stop school attendance
description: Hundreds of female pupils in Iran have been subjected to poisoning attacks in classrooms in what is believed to be an attempt to stop them attending school.

title: The solution to long-distance relationships? A virtual kissing machine
description: A remote kissing device has been created by a group of university students in China for people in long-distance relationships.

title: Footballer who rushed to aid of unconscious opponent honoured with FIFA award
description: A footballer whose quick thinking potentially saved the life of a seriously injured opponent has been honoured with an award by FIFA.

title: After model's legs were found in a fridge, police search landfill for missing body parts
description: Police are searching a landfill site as they investigate the murder of a Hong Kong model whose dismembered legs were found inside a fridge.

title: The moon could get its own time zone, but clocks work differently there – here's why
description: Most of us have at some point stopped to gaze up at the moon - but have you ever wondered what time it is up there?

title: Shots fired near German primary school leaving one adult critically injured
description: One person has been critically injured after a shooting near a German primary school, according to police.

title: Missing man found in shark's stomach after family identifies his tattoo
description: The remains of a man who disappeared earlier this month appear to have been found inside a shark.

title: US asks Mexico to extradite son of Joaquin 'El Chapo' Guzman
description: The US has asked Mexico to extradite Ovidio Guzman, son of notorious drug boss Joaquin "El Chapo" Guzman.
